eef0 us_animate_this align_none"><a ref="magnificPopup" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IMG_0743-1-scaled.jpg" aria-label="IMG_0743-1" class="w-image-h"><img decoding="async" width="1920" height="1280" src="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IMG_0743-1-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IMG_0743-1-scaled.jpg 1920w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IMG_0743-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IMG_0743-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IMG_0743-1-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IMG_0743-1-1320x880.jpg 1320w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a></div><div class="w-image us_custom_74339363 us_animate_this align_none"><a ref="magnificPopup" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GT0A7339-1.jpg" aria-label="GT0A7339-1" class="w-image-h"><img decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" src="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GT0A7339-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GT0A7339-1.jpg 1920w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GT0A7339-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GT0A7339-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GT0A7339-1-600x338.jpg 600w, https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GT0A7339-1-1320x743.jpg 1320w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="l-section wpb_row height_small width_full"><div class="l-section-h i-cf"><div class="g-cols vc_row via_grid cols_2 laptops-cols_inherit tablets-cols_inherit mobiles-cols_1 valign_top type_default stacking_default"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="w-btn-wrapper align_justify"><a class="w-btn us-btn-style_11 icon_atleft" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/restaurant-seven-speisekarte.pdf"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i><span class="w-btn-label">Speisekarte ansehen</span></a></div><div class="w-btn-wrapper align_justify"><a class="w-btn us-btn-style_11 icon_atleft" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/milo-speisekarte-02-2025-dessert_final.pdf"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i><span class="w-btn-label">Dessertkarte ansehen</span></a></div><div class="wpb_text_column"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h1></h1>
<h1>FRÜHSTÜCK-Buffet</h1>
<p>Freuen Sie sich auf ein reichhaltiges Frühstücksbuffet, mit Produkten ausgewählter Produzenten, aus der Region Villach und Umgebung! <strong>All you can eat | € 24,90 (Kinder bis 6-12 Jahre € 12,90, 3-6 Jahre € 9,90)</strong></p>
</div></div><div class="w-slider style_none fit_scaledown nav_none count_5"><div class="w-slider-h" aria-hidden="true"><div class="royalSlider"><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" data-rsw="1024" data-rsh="683" data-rsbigimg="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC08251-scaled.jpg" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC08251-1024x683.jpg"><span data-alt=""></span></a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" data-rsw="1024" data-rsh="683" data-rsbigimg="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC07866-scaled.jpg" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC07866-1024x683.jpg"><span data-alt=""></span></a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" data-rsw="1024" data-rsh="683" data-rsbigimg="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC07907-scaled.jpg" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC07907-1024x683.jpg"><span data-alt=""></span></a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" data-rsw="1024" data-rsh="683" data-rsbigimg="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC08235-scaled.jpg" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC08235-1024x683.jpg"><span data-alt=""></span></a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" data-rsw="1024" data-rsh="683" data-rsbigimg="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC07902-scaled.jpg" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC07902-1024x683.jpg"><span data-alt=""></span></a></div></div><img decoding="async" src="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DSC08251-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt loading="lazy"></div><div class="w-slider-json" onclick='return {&quot;autoScaleSlider&quot;:true,&quot;addActiveClass&quot;:true,&quot;loop&quot;:true,&quot;fadeInLoadedSlide&quot;:false,&quot;slidesSpacing&quot;:0,&quot;imageScalePadding&quot;:0,&quot;numImagesToPreload&quot;:2,&quot;arrowsNav&quot;:true,&quot;arrowsNavAutoHide&quot;:false,&quot;transitionType&quot;:&quot;move&quot;,&quot;transitionSpeed&quot;:500,&quot;block&quot;:{&quot;moveEffect&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;speed&quot;:300},&quot;thumbs&quot;:{&quot;fitInViewport&quot;:false,&quot;firstMargin&quot;:false,&quot;spacing&quot;:4},&quot;controlNavigation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;autoplay&quot;:{&quot;enabled&quot;:true,&quot;pauseOnHover&quot;:true,&quot;delay&quot;:3000},&quot;fullscreen&quot;:{&quot;enabled&quot;:true},&quot;autoScaleSliderWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;autoScaleSliderHeight&quot;:683}'></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="w-btn-wrapper align_justify"><a class="w-btn us-btn-style_11 icon_atleft" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Milo-Barkarte_2024-07-29.pdf"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i><span class="w-btn-label">Barkarte ansehen</span></a></div><div class="w-btn-wrapper align_justify"><a class="w-btn us-btn-style_11 icon_atleft" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.hotel-seven.at/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Milo-Fruehstueckskarte_Juli_2025.pdf"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i><span class="w-btn-label">Frühstückskarte ansehen</span></a></div><div class="wpb_text_column"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h1></h1>
<h1>FRÜHSTÜCK à la carte</h1>
<p>Von Montag bis Freitag von 6.30 Uhr bis 10.30 Uhr sowie wochenends von 7.00 Uhr bis 11.00 Uhr bieten wir unseren Gästen die Möglichkeit auch à la carte zu frühstücken.</p>
<p>Die Frühstückskarte enthält ein breites Angebot für jeden Gusto!</p>
<p>Entscheiden Sie sich für Ihr Lieblingsfrühstück – klassisch, gesund oder herzhaft – und bestellen Sie ganz nach Wunsch Eierspeisen wie Omelette oder Rührei.</p>
<article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-24" data-scroll-anchor="true">
<div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 &#091;--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)&#093; @&#091;37rem&#093;:&#091;--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)&#093; @&#091;72rem&#093;:&#091;--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)&#093; px-(--thread-content-margin)">
<div class="&#091;--thread-content-max-width:32rem&#093; @&#091;34rem&#093;:&#091;--thread-content-max-width:40rem&#093; @&#091;64rem&#093;:&#091;--thread-content-max-width:48rem&#093; mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1">
<div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn">
<div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3">
<div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow">
<div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal &#091;.text-message+&amp;&#093;:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="7347e81f-536a-4792-a96a-60064365a894" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4-1-mini">
<div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-&#091;3px&#093;">
<div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling markdown-new-styling-hidden-hrs">
<p data-start="0" data-end="88" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Genießen Sie Ihr Frühstück in entspannter Atmosphäre, ganz nach Ihrer persönlichen Wahl und lassen Sie sich von unserem Serviceteam verwöhnen.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
