</article>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="l-section wpb_row height_small width_full color_primary"><div class="l-section-overlay" style="background:#b17e09"></div><div class="l-section-h i-cf"><div class="g-cols vc_row via_grid cols_1 laptops-cols_inherit tablets-cols_inherit mobiles-cols_1 valign_top type_default stacking_default"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="g-cols wpb_row via_grid cols_2 laptops-cols_inherit tablets-cols_inherit mobiles-cols_1 valign_top type_default stacking_default" style="--columns-gap:3rem;"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_text_column"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h2>Milo Restaurant</h2>
<ul>
<li>Sonnige Terrasse</li>
<li>Gratis Parkplätze</li>
<li>Moderne, regionale á la carte Küche</li>
<li>Mittagsmenüs</li>
<li>Weihnachtsfeiern / Hochzeitsfeiern / Geburtstagsfeiern</li>
<li>Seminare</li>
<li>Bar</li>
</ul>
<p><b>Wir treffen uns im „Milo“!</b></p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_text_column"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h3>Öffnungszeiten und Reservierungen</h3>
<p><strong>Frühstücksbuffet </strong>und<strong> á la carte Frühstück<br />
</strong>Montag bis Freitag von 06:30 bis 10:30 Uhr<br />
Samstag, Sonntag und feiertags von 07:00 bis 11:00 Uhr<strong><br />
Milo Restaurant</strong> &#8211; Küche bis 22:00 Uhr<br />
<strong>Milo Bar</strong> &#8211; bis 24:00 Uhr</p>
<p><b>Reserviere deinen Tisch im Milo<br />
</b>+43 4242 37 000 &#8211; 703<br />
<a href="mailto:restaurant@hotel-seven.at">restaurant@hotel-seven.at</a></p>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="l-section wpb_row height_small width_full"><div class="l-section-h i-cf"><div class="g-cols vc_row via_grid cols_1 laptops-cols_inherit tablets-cols_inherit mobiles-cols_1 valign_top type_default stacking_default"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="w-grid us_grid type_grid layout_gallery_default cols_2 preload_style_spinner" id="us_grid_1" style="--columns:2;" data-filterable="true"><style>@media (max-width:1380px){#us_grid_1{--columns:1!important}}.layout_gallery_default .w-grid-item-h{}</style><div class="w-grid-list">	<article class="w-grid-item size_1x1 post-6806 attachment type-attachment status-inherit hentry" data-id="6806">
